 calorie; avoid excess", "pregnancy_safe": "Yes", "evidence_level": "Traditional"}, {"id": "REM005", "name_english": "Soaked Black Raisins", "name_hindi": "भीगे हुए काले किशमिश", "category": "Anemia", "ingredients": "[\"Black raisins (10-15)\", \"Water (1 cup)\"]", "preparation": "1. Soak raisins overnight\n2. Eat in morning along with water", "dosage": "Daily on empty stomach", "warnings": "Diabetics should limit intake", "pregnancy_safe": "Yes", "evidence_level": "Moderate"}, {"id": "REM006", "name_english": "Palak Dal", "name_hindi": "पालक दाल", "category": "Anemia", "ingredients": "[\"Spinach (1 cup)\", \"Toor dal (1/2 cup)\", \"Garlic (3 cloves)\", \"Turmeric (1/2 tsp)\"]", "preparation": "1. Cook dal and spinach together\n2. Add garlic tempering\n3. Simmer well", "dosage": "1 serving daily", "warnings": "Avoid excess if kidney issues (oxalates)", "pregnancy_safe": "Yes", "evidence_level": "Moderate"}, {"id": "REM007", "name_english": "Ragi Malt", "name_hindi": "रागी माल्ट", "category": "Anemia", "ingredients": "[\"Ragi flour (2 tbsp)\", \"Milk (1 cup)\", \"Jaggery (1 tbsp)\", \"Cardamom (pinch)\"]", "preparation": "1. Cook ragi flour with water\n2. Add milk and jaggery\n3. Stir until thick\n4. Add cardamom", "dosage": "1 cup daily", "warnings": "Ensure proper cooking to avoid indigestion", "pregnancy_safe": "Yes", "evidence_level": "Strong"}, {"id": "REM008", "name_english": "Pomegranate Juice", "name_hindi": "अनार का जूस", "category": "Anemia", "ingredients": "[\"Pomegranate (1)\", \"Honey (1 tsp)\", \"Black salt (pinch)\"]", "preparation": "1. Extract juice from pomegranate\n2. Add honey and salt\n3. Mix well", "dosage": "1 glass daily", "warnings": "Avoid added sugar if diabetic", "pregnancy_safe": "Yes", "evidence_level": "Moderate"}, {"id": "REM009", "name_english": "Amla Murabba", "name_hindi": "आंवला मुरब्बा", "category": "Anemia", "ingredients": "[\"Amla (500g)\", \"Sugar syrup\"]", "preparation": "1. Boil amla and soak in sugar syrup\n2. Store for long-term use", "dosage": "1 piece daily", "warnings": "High sugar content", "pregnancy_safe": "Yes", "evidence_level": "Traditional"}, {"id": "REM010", "name_english": "Date-Walnut Milkshake", "name_hindi": "खजूर-अखरोट मिल्कशेक", "category": "Anemia", "ingredients": "[\"Dates (4-5)\", \"Walnuts (2)\", \"Milk (1 cup)\", \"Saffron (few strands)\"]", "preparation": "1. Blend all ingredients\n2. Serve fresh", "dosage": "1 glass daily", "warnings": "High calorie drink", "pregnancy_safe": "Yes", "evidence_level": "Moderate"}, {"id": "REM011", "name_english": "Bajra Khichdi", "name_hindi": "बाजरा खिचड़ी", "category": "Anemia", "ingredients": "[\"Pearl millet (1/2 cup)\", \"Green moong dal (1/2 cup)\", \"Ghee (1 tbsp)\"]", "preparation": "1. Cook millet and dal together\n2. Add ghee before serving", "dosage": "1 serving daily (winter)", "warnings": "Heavy for digestion if overeaten", "pregnancy_safe": "Yes", "evidence_level": "Traditional"}, {"id": "REM012", "name_english": "Sargi Drink", "name_hindi": "सरगी पेय", "category": "Anemia", "ingredients": "[\"Soaked almonds (5)\", \"Milk (1 cup)\", \"Dates (2-3)\", \"Saffron (few strands)\"]", "preparation": "1. Blend all ingredients\n2. Consume early morning", "dosage": "Once before fasting", "warnings": "Consult doctor if gestational diabetes", "pregnancy_safe": "Yes", "evidence_level": "Traditional"}, {"id": "REM013", "name_english": "Liver Masala", "name_hindi": "लीवर मसाला", "category": "Anemia", "ingredients": "[\"Chicken/mutton liver (200g)\", \"Onion\", \"Tomato\", \"Spices\"]", "preparation": "1. Cook liver with spices\n2. Ensure proper cooking", "dosage": "Once weekly", "warnings": "Avoid excess vitamin A intake during pregnancy", "pregnancy_safe": "Limited (consult doctor)", "evidence_level": "Strong"}, {"id": "REM014", "name_english": "Halim Seed Drink", "name_hindi": "हलीम बीज पेय", "category": "Anemia", "ingredients": "[\"Garden cress seeds (1 tbsp)\", \"Milk (1 cup)\", \"Jaggery (1 tbsp)\"]", "preparation": "1. Soak