ecially in first trimester", "warnings": "Contains latex which may stimulate uterine contractions and increase miscarriage risk", "pregnancy_safe": "No (1st trimester)", "evidence_level": "Moderate"}, {"id": "REM035", "name_english": "Pineapple", "name_hindi": "अनानास", "category": "Pregnancy Contraindications", "ingredients": "[\"Pineapple\"]", "preparation": "Consume only in small amounts if at all", "dosage": "Avoid in 1st trimester; moderate intake later", "warnings": "Contains bromelain which may soften cervix in high amounts", "pregnancy_safe": "Limited (avoid early pregnancy)", "evidence_level": "Moderate"}, {"id": "REM036", "name_english": "Sesame Seeds (Excess)", "name_hindi": "तिल (अधिक मात्रा)", "category": "Pregnancy Contraindications", "ingredients": "[\"Sesame seeds\"]", "preparation": "Use in small culinary amounts only", "dosage": "Avoid excess especially in 1st trimester", "warnings": "Traditionally considered uterine stimulant in large quantities", "pregnancy_safe": "Limited", "evidence_level": "Traditional"}, {"id": "REM037", "name_english": "Ginger Turmeric Milk", "name_hindi": "अदरक-हल्दी दूध", "category": "Respiratory Health", "ingredients": "[\"Ginger\", \"Turmeric\", \"Milk\", \"Black pepper\"]", "preparation": "Boil milk with ginger, turmeric and black pepper", "dosage": "1 cup at night", "warnings": "Avoid excess turmeric in early pregnancy", "pregnancy_safe": "Yes (moderate)", "evidence_level": "Moderate"}, {"id": "REM038", "name_english": "Tulsi Kadha", "name_hindi": "तुलसी काढ़ा", "category": "Respiratory Health", "ingredients": "[\"Tulsi leaves\", \"Ginger\", \"Black pepper\", \"Cinnamon\"]", "preparation": "Boil all ingredients in water until reduced", "dosage": "1 cup daily", "warnings": "Avoid excessive intake", "pregnancy_safe": "Yes (moderate)", "evidence_level": "Strong"}, {"id": "REM039", "name_english": "Honey Tulsi Mix", "name_hindi": "शहद-तुलसी मिश्रण", "category": "Respiratory Health", "ingredients": "[\"Honey\", \"Tulsi leaf